        <coverage scope="document">
            <geographicCoverage scope="document">
                <geographicDescription>The site (LU7B) is located at 700m in elevation and consist of a 1km long transect along the walking track along Robson Creek which runs parallel to the Mt Edith Road. There are 6 individual sampling points, located at every 200m interval along this transect, (LU7B1, LU7B2, LU7B3, LU7B4, LU7B5 and LU7B6), which are flagged and marked with reflectors for easier detection.</geographicDescription>
